- Ensure well structured folders, put components in components folder.
- Reference the readme.md file for project overview.
- Always use @ alias for imports when possible.
- Always use kebab-case when creating a files.
- Always use tailwindcss for styling.
- Don't use template string for classNames use cn() util from "@lib/utils" instead.
- Never use `any` typescript keyword.
- Use collocation in folder structure
- Put global components in /app/\_components folder
- refer to the readme.md file for project overview.
- Always use single responsibility principle for components. The page should only display subcomponents. Each subcomponent should have its own file.

- Do not create logic you were not asked for.
- Do not add unnecessary comments for obvious things and logic.
